STRING 49998
{
You can use the corresponding AI gold / exp bonus adjustment command mode to control mode selection when computers get money and experience rate, money and experience to adjust the adjustment can be invoked simultaneously.

Experience plus adjustments:
|c00dd8dff Default |r: According to the difficulty, AI would be +20% / 45% / 80% extra experience.
|c00dd8dff-normexp (-ne) |r: AI will no longer get any extra experience bonus.
|c00dd8dff-highexp (-he) |r: Depending on the degree of difficulty, AI will get an extra bonus of a different experience, an increase of +40% default / 70% / 110%.
|c00dd8dff-dynaexp (-de) |r: Dynamic AI is empirical mode --- each kill, their experience will get access to additional rate (50 +5 * Number of main enemy players)% increase every three minutes if. AI do not kill enemy heroes is the experience gained by its extra rate will be increased by 17.5%, while each time the AI get kill / assists, additional experience gained will reduce the rate of 33% / 25%. AI can get a total of up to 200% of the additional experience.
Money Bonus adjustment:
|c00dd8dff Default |r: According to the difficulty, AI will get bonus every 7 seconds, and a small amount of extra money 0/4/8 initial money.
|c00dd8dff-normgold (-ng) |r: AI no longer get any extra money.
|c00dd8dff-highgold (-hg) |r: Every seven seconds to get extra money 8, the initial money to +10%.
|c00dd8dff-dynagold (-dg) |r: Dynamic Money Mode --- each AI has been killed, it will enhance the speed of money to get 5/7 seconds every three minutes if not kill the enemy AI heroes enhance +2.5. when / 7 seconds (from the start of the game the first five minutes counting), while AI get every kill / assists, extra money to get the lower rate of 33% / 25%. AI can get the maximum total of 72 gold every 7 seconds extra money .
The manner described above is called mixed mode command:
|c00dd8dff-beginnermode (-bm) Novice Mode |r: equivalent to normexp + normgold
|c00dd8dff-advancedmode (-am) Advanced Mode |r: equivalent to normexp + normgold + dynaexp + dynagold
|c00dd8dff-xtrememode (-xm) play off |r: equivalent to normexp + normgold + dynaexp + dynagold, but the dynamic part of the increase will be higher. 
}
