AI map update and development progress, please refer to http://dota-pbmn.blogspot.com/(Status: |cffFF0000Unknown\Missing in Action|r). Note: Since 2014, The Current AI Maintainers are listed below. You can visit the PlayDota forum and go to the AI thread or you can visit this site for updates: http://jamesdruid.blogspot.com/

The New AI Map Maintainers: |cffFF0000JoyJ|r and |cff0000FFJames Druid|r

Very Big Thanks to |cffFF0000JoyJ|r for continuing the development of the AI map. He completely restructured the map(from 6.78) and turned it into the latest DotA version(6.81). 
}
